                            <comment id="17777053" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 19 Oct 2023 06:35:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1913106 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
